==個人生活==
[[File:SFGiants_30.png|thumb]]
1990年代初，隨著塞佩沙的名人堂票選年份即將屆滿，許多球星也發起請願希望大聯盟將他入主古柏鎮。1994年，塞佩沙只差7票就能入選名人堂。而他也因為連續15年投票未達門檻而被取消票選資格。1999年，他透過名人堂資深委員會推薦，終於入選名人堂。他也成為繼[[羅伯托·克萊門特|羅伯托·克萊門特]]第二位入選名人堂的波多黎各人。

此外，塞佩沙也入選了13個運動名人堂，其中包含：灣區運動名人堂、波多黎各運動名人堂、密蘇里運動名人堂、非裔美國人運動名人堂、舊金山巨人名人堂等等。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.bashof.org/inducteebios/ocepeda.htm| title=Inductees: Orlando Cepeda| publisher=Bay Area Sports Hall of Fame| accessdate=2008-08-08| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430124404/http://www.bashof.org/inducteebios/ocepeda.htm| archivedate=2008-04-30| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="p.209">Fagen et al., p.209</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.mosportshalloffame.com/inductee_detail/Orlando+Cepeda/232| title=Inductee Detail: Orlando Cepeda| publisher=Missouri Sports Hall of Fame| accessdate=2008-08-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525092827/http://www.mosportshalloffame.com/inductee_detail/Orlando+Cepeda/232| archive-date=2011-05-25| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.hispanicbaseballmuseum.com/fme_cepeda.html| title=Hall of Fame: Orlando Cepeda| publisher=Hispanic Heritage Baseball Museum| accessdate=2008-08-08| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090109111628/http://www.hispanicbaseballmuseum.com/fme_cepeda.html| archivedate=2009-01-09| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://usfdons.cstv.com/genrel/020807aab.html| title=Debra Gore-Mann to Be Inducted in African American Ethnic Sports Hall of Fame Friday| publisher=University of San Francisco Athletic| date=2007-02-08| accessdate=2008-08-08| archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120717032014/http://usfdons.cstv.com/genrel/020807aab.html| archivedate=2012-07-17| dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2018年2月，他因為跌倒而一度住院。之後他在加州的某處停車場跌倒引發中風再次住院，不過所幸健康出院。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Shea |first1=John |title=Orlando Cepeda attends first Giants game since traumatic fall: it’s ‘like coming home’ |url=https://m.sfgate.com/giants/article/Orlando-Cepeda-attends-first-Giants-game-since-13053182.php |website=Sfgate.com |publisher=Hearst |accessdate=October 10, 2018 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329172714/https://m.sfgate.com/giants/article/Orlando-Cepeda-attends-first-Giants-game-since-13053182.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>
